import React from 'react' import '../Vehicle/Vehicle.css'; import { Link } from 'react-router-dom'; import axios from 'axios'; import { useNavigate } from 'react-router-dom'; function Vehicle(props) { const {_id,vin,regNo,make,model,year,ownerName,ownerNic,ownerEmail,ownerAddress,contactNo} = props.vehicle; const history = useNavigate(); const deleteHandler = async()=>{ await axios.delete(`http://localhost:5000/vehicles/${_id}`) .then(res=>res.data) .then(() =>history("/")) .then(() =>history("/vehicledetails")); } return (
ID VIN Reg.No Make Model Year Owner Name Owner NIC Owner Email Owner Address Contact Number
{_id} {vin} {regNo} {make} {model} {year} {ownerName} {ownerNic} {ownerEmail} {ownerAddress} {contactNo} Update
) } export default Vehicle
